title._content: A juvenile shrimp being raised at the University of Arizona Environmental Research Laboratory at Tucson..., 04/1974.

description._content: Original Caption: A juvenile shrimp being raised at the University of Arizona Environmental Research Laboratory at Tucson in their high intensity aquaculture experiments. They have halved the time it takes the shrimp to breed, hatch and mature in its normal ocean habitat, 04/1974.
